   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,138:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  As a kid, I played historical strategy video games, like Civilization. This shows you how
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,139:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: civilization formed. Through the technology tree, you invent different things. You
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,139:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
