   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,146:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  小时候，我玩历史策略视频游戏，比如《文明》。这向你展示了文明是如何形成的。通过科技树，你发明不同的东西。你会发明读写能力、民主和火药。你开始意识到，
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,147:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 哦哇，技术有阶段。没有创造读写能力就不可能有民主。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 技术和思想发展有阶段。这是一个有用的框架。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,148:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,158:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  It is important to view knowledge as a semantic tree. Make sure you understand the
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,161:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: fundamental principles (the trunk and big branches) before you get into the leaves (the details), then
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,162:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: there is something for them to hang on to.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,162:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:51,162:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  将知识视为语义树很重要。在深入叶子（细节）之前，确保你理解基本原理（树干和大树枝），这样它们才有东西可以依附。
