   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,344:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  逆境塑造了我。我的疼痛阈值变得非常高。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,345:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Eat Glass and Stare into the Abyss
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,345:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 吃玻璃并凝视深渊
