   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,346:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  When starting a company, usually the beginning is fun. Then, it
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,347:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,347:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s hellish for a number of
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,348:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: years.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,348:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,349:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  创办公司时，通常开始很有趣。然后，会有几年是地狱般的。
