   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,354:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,356:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,356:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: not. There are periods of fun, and there are periods where it
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,357:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,357:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s just awful.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,358:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,358:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  创办公司时，你必须专注于短期和资金流入，否则公司会死。人们想，
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,358:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,359:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 哦，创办公司会很有趣。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,359:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,360:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 不是的。有有趣的时期，也有非常糟糕的时期。
