   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,362:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: My friend Bill Lee says, 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,363:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,363:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Starting a company is like eating glass and staring into the abyss.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,364:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
