   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,366:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,367:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  你必须感到相当有冲动去创办公司。你必须有高疼痛阈值。我的朋友比尔·李说，
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,367:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,367:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 创办公司就像吃玻璃并凝视深渊。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,368:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,368:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 这有些道理。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,369:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,369:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,369:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,370:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Staring into the abyss
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,370:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,371:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,371:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  means you
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,372:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
