   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,378:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: t get this right, the company will die.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,379:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,379:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  This can be quite stressful.
