   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,380:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,380:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,381:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 凝视深渊
