   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,383:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 如果我不把这做好，公司就会死。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,383:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,384:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 这可能非常有压力。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,384:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,385:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,385:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,386:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Eating glass
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,386:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,386:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  means you
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,387:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,392:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ve got to work on the problems the company needs you to work
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,393:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: on, not the problems you want to work on. You end up working on problems you wish you weren
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,393:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
