   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,394:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: working on. That
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,395:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,395:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,396:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,396:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: eating glass,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,397:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,397:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and it goes on for a long time.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,398:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,398:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,399:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,399:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 吃玻璃
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,400:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,400:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 意味着你必须处理公司需要你处理的问题，而不是你想处理的问题。你最终在处理你希望不必处理的问题。那就是
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,401:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
