   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,402:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ，它会持续很长时间。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,403:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,403:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  We were facing imminent death at SpaceX, Tesla, and SolarCity for a long time. We
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,404:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,407:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: re no
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,407:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: longer staring directly into the abyss, which is great. It is there in the distance, but I
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,408:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,409:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: m not staring
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,409:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: right at it. There
