   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,411:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s always going to be some amount of glass that has to be chewed. But it
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:03:52,411:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
