   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,863:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ELON
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,864:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,866:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: S RECOMMENDED READING
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,867:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 埃隆的推荐书单
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,867:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,868:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Expose yourself to as many smart people as possible. Read a lot of books.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,869:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,869:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  尽可能多地接触聪明人。读很多书。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,870:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: BOOKS
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,870:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 书籍
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,870:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,874:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Since there are so many links in this section, you may prefer a digital version. Go to
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,874:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ElonMuskBook.org to get a digital version of this chapter.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,875:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  由于本节有很多链接，你可能更喜欢数字版本。前往 ElonMuskBook.org 获取本章的数字版本。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,876:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: FICTION
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,876:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 小说
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,876:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The Hitchhiker
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,877:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,877:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s Guide to the Galaxy by Douglas Adams
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,878:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,878:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 《银河系漫游指南》道格拉斯·亚当斯
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,878:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,880:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  This is in fact a book of philosophy, disguised as a silly humor book. If you read it from
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,881:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: the standpoint of 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,881:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,882:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Wow, this is an interesting book of philosophy,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,882:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,884:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  it is quite insightful. It hits this
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,885:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: point: The answer is easy once you can properly formulate the question.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,886:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,886:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  这实际上是一本哲学书，伪装成愚蠢的幽默书。如果你从
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,892:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,893:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 哇，这是一本有趣的哲学书
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,893:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,894:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 的角度阅读它，它很有见地。它击中这一点：一旦你能正确地提出问题，答案就很容易。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,894:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,908:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  It also makes fun of bureaucracy. Earth essentially gets destroyed by a sort of clerical
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,912:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: error. Aliens decide they need an interstellar highway and Earth is in the way. They post the fact that
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,913:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Earth needs to get destroyed for this interstellar highway, but of course, it
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,914:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,915:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s posted on an alien
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,916:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: bulletin board that no one on Earth can access.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,916:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,916:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  它还取笑官僚主义。地球基本上被一种文书错误摧毁。外星人决定他们需要一条星际公路，地球挡住了路。他们发布了地球需要被摧毁以建造这条星际公路的事实，但当然，它发布在一个地球上没有人能访问的外星公告板上。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,917:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The Lord of the Rings by J.R.R. Tolkien
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,917:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,918:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 《指环王》J.R.R. 托尔金
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,918:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,919:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  I know it
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,919:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,920:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s cliché, but The Lord of the Rings is my favorite series ever.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,920:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,921:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  我知道这是陈词滥调，但《指环王》是我有史以来最喜欢的系列。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,921:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Foundation series by Isaac Asimov
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,922:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,922:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 《基地》系列 艾萨克·阿西莫夫
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,923:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,924:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  I recommend reading the Foundation series. It
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,924:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,924:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s about how there
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,925:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,927:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s likely to be another dark
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,928:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: age, which my guess is there will be at some point. I
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,928:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,929:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: m not predicting that we
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,929:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,930:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: re about to enter a dark
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,930:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: age, but that there
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,931:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,931:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s some probability we will, particularly if there
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,932:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,933:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s a third world war. We want to
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,933:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: make sure that there
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,934:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,937:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s enough of us as a seed of human civilization somewhere else to bring
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,938:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: civilization back and perhaps shorten the length of a dark age.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,938:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,939:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  我建议阅读《基地》系列。它是关于可能会有另一个黑暗时代，我的猜测是某个时候会有。我不是预测我们即将进入黑暗时代，而是有一些可能性我们会，特别是如果有第三次世界大战。我们想确保我们有足够多的人作为人类文明的种子在别处，以带回文明并可能缩短黑暗时代的长度。
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,939:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English:
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,940:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  It
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,940:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,941:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s unlikely we
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,941:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,942:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ll never have another world war. There probably will be at some point. I
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,943:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,943:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: m
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,944:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: not predicting this, but given
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,944:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 中文：
   DEBUG: 2026-03-26 20:04:05,945:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  我们永远不会再有世界大战是不可能的。可能在某个时候会有。我不是在预测这个，但鉴于
